reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice quality for the price!
reviews.reviewText: Great functional End Table that is really sturdy! The only downside are the poor directions. The bottom bars to hold drawers…be careful you place them correctly, and put the little magazine type pouch on before putting the table top on. Otherwise assembly was fairly easy!

reviews.reviewText: I got this for my bathroom to store toiletries and toilet paper. It works great and can store a lot of items. I’m a big fan of the rustic burnt wood look. It has fabric drawers which is perfect for a high humidity environment like a bathroom. Over I’m very happy with it.
